channel.title: [PI] Run Error
channel.description:
Not sure what I'm doing wrong, but I get this error when I run: [code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ExceptionInInitializerError Caused by: java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 16 at server.world.ItemHandler.loadItemList(ItemHandler.java:377) at server.world.ItemHandler.<init>(ItemHandler.java:34) at server.Server.<clinit>(Server.java:62) Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
I recently added a few new items, correctly added the models and cases, made sure I added them properly into Items.cfg and I'm still getting this error. Any ideas?
